p: Functional enrichment analysis of DEG was performed with Enrichr analysis tool ( http://amp.pharm.mssm.edu/Enrichr/). To associate a set of differentially expressed genes with a functional biological term, Gene Ontology terms were assigned using GO biological processes 2017b annotation set. GO terms were ranked by a combined score (ln(P-value) Ã— Z-score); the P-value computed using the Fisher exact test.
